---
import { TextSection, Button } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
import HeroSection from '../../components/sections/heros/HeroSection.astro';

const seo = {
	title: 'About Deepline | We are fixing the hardest entry point in ML: setup',
	description: 'Deepline is building the entry point to production ML by removing setup complexity in pipelines.',
};
---

<Layout {seo}>
	<HeroSection>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>We are fixing the hardest entry point in ML: setup</h1>
			<p>
				Deepline is building the entry point to production ML by removing setup complexity in pipelines. Today we focus on simplifying Airflow + MLflow setup; later we will expand into monitoring, retraining, and portability.
			</p>
		</div>
		<picture slot="image-container">
			<img
				src="/assets/images/home/classic-hero.jpg"
				alt="Deepline Team"
				id="about-hero-image"
			/>
		</picture>
	</HeroSection>
	
	<TextSection narrow>
		<h2>The Thesis</h2>
		
		<h3>The Problem</h3>
		<p>Pipeline setup is slow, brittle, and inconsistent. Teams waste weeks on configuration before they can focus on the actual machine learning work that drives value.</p>
		
		<h3>Why Existing Tools Fail</h3>
		<p>Current solutions create vendor lock-in, require extensive manual configurations, and introduce too many moving parts. This complexity compounds over time, creating operational debt before teams even reach production.</p>
		
		<h3>Our Contrarian View</h3>
		<p>We believe you should start with setup, build credibility with immediate value, and then layer in monitoring and retraining capabilities. Most platforms try to solve everything at once - we focus on the sharpest pain point first.</p>

		<h2>What We Are Building</h2>
		<p><strong>Today:</strong> A setup simplification layer for Airflow and MLflow that reduces weeks of configuration to a single YAML file and two commands.</p>
		<p><strong>Tomorrow:</strong> Our roadmap expands into three key phases - Observe (monitoring and drift detection), Adapt (safe retraining workflows), and Port (cloud-agnostic deployment).</p>

		<h2>Roadmap</h2>
		<div class="roadmap-timeline">
			<div class="roadmap-item">
				<strong>Q4 2025:</strong> Public beta (setup automation for tabular + time series)
			</div>
			<div class="roadmap-item">
				<strong>Q1 2026:</strong> Monitoring and drift detection
			</div>
			<div class="roadmap-item">
				<strong>Q1 2026:</strong> Retraining workflows + on-prem runner
			</div>
		</div>

		<h2>Team</h2>
		<div class="team-members">
			<div class="team-member">
				<h3>Taimoor, Founder & CEO</h3>
				<p>Data Scientist and AI Engineer, leading Deepline to eliminate ML pipeline setup complexity.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="team-member">
				<h3>Abdul, Chief of Engineering</h3>
				<p>Systems design engineer, leading technical architecture and execution.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<h2>Operating Principles</h2>
		<ol class="principles-list">
			<li>Solve the sharpest pain first</li>
			<li>Truth over status</li>
			<li>Quantify or delete</li>
			<li>Default to automation</li>
			<li>Portability first</li>
		</ol>
	</TextSection>
</Layout>

<style>
	.roadmap-timeline {
		margin: 1.5rem 0;
		padding-left: 1rem;
		border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-primary);
	}

	.roadmap-item {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		padding-left: 1rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.roadmap-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: -8px;
		top: 8px;
		width: 12px;
		height: 12px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--theme-primary);
	}

	.team-members {
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.team-member {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--theme-surface-1);
		border-radius: var(--theme-shape-radius);
	}

	.team-member h3 {
		color: var(--theme-on-surface-1);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.team-member p {
		color: var(--theme-on-surface-1);
		margin: 0;
	}

	.principles-list {
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		margin: 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.principles-list li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.cta-section {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		background: var(--theme-surface-2);
		border-radius: var(--theme-shape-radius);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-section h2 {
		color: var(--theme-on-surface-2);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.cta-description {
		color: var(--theme-on-surface-2);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.roadmap-timeline {
			padding-left: 0.5rem;
		}
		
		.roadmap-item {
			padding-left: 0.5rem;
		}
		
		.team-member {
			padding: 1rem;
		}
		
		.cta-section {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>